name: boobcrush
description:
I'm terrible at names. This LoRA model generates characters lying down with enormous breasts that are flopping to the sides. However it seems to do standing/sitting poses as well.

*V3 Change Log*

  • seems to allow slightly larger sizes now with "gigantic breasts"

  • more consistent generations overall, but always a roll of the dice

  • removed images with hands holding breasts to reduce stray fingers in gens (Not sure how effective it was)

  • added "clothed" tag, hopefully it works better with clothing now

  • added more images to training

"pregnant" tag is optional, but seems to work well if you are into that kind of thing

Tips:

  • Use "boobcrush" in combination with "huge breasts" using landscape aspect for the largest breast sizes

  • Use portrait images for more reasonable sized breasts, or exclude "huge breasts"

  • This model probably prefers nudity, and laying down/sitting up positions

modelVersions.description:

  • LR 1e-4

  • base model Av3

  • flip aug

  • tokens 225
